      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "TIL HEAVENS ROCKN NZ (1) led from this barrier and boxed on for third last start at this circuit and distance, beaten 3 metres. Eases back a little in grade and could be hard to catch. MICKEYS RUN (9) is back from a spell of four-and-a-half months and looks to be right up to the mark following a placing in a recent trial. No favours expected from this draw but it is worth noting he kicked off his last campaign win a Newcastle win. RUMOUR STRIDE (6) did a good job in coming from the outside barrier and finishing runner-up at Newcastle last time out. Draws a couple of spots lower and won the only time she attempted this circuit and distance. PETES BIG JIM (2) draws well so could bounce back.",
